Task Content:
For the BARTH Face Powder registration, I will be requiring Testing method for testing of BARTH face Powder. Please see the following points which needs to be in the report:
1)Microbiological quality check to ensure the absence of microbial counts and pathogens;
2)Qualitative and quantitative estimation of active ingredients;
3)Physical testing which includes parameters such as viscosity, spread-ability, scratch test, pay-off test;
4)Skin irritation and sensitivity studies;
5) Physical and chemical analysis of raw materials and active ingredients;
6)Safety tests to assess the presence of heavy metals in cosmetics, banned colours and chemicals;

